# Responsive Landing Page

A clean and modern **responsive landing page** built using only **HTML5** and **CSS3**. Designed to adapt seamlessly across devices — from desktops to tablets to mobile phones — without using any frameworks or JavaScript.

---

## 🛠️ Technologies Used

- HTML5
- CSS3 (Flexbox & Media Queries)

---

## 📱 Features

- Fully responsive layout
- Clean and modern design
- Mobile-first approach
- CSS Flexbox and media query based responsiveness
- Easy to customize and extend

---

